<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'>S=
ome
messages reveal previously unknown locations. For your convenience, these
locations are indicated in the galaxy view by a dashed blue expanding
&#8220;ping&#8221; circle. Once these locations have been explored the
&#8220;ping&#8221; circle will disappear.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

